parameters: The slime gets deeper here as it leads you down into the tunnel that connects these slime tunnels with the rest of the dungeon. Do you want to head back?

As you are walking along, you encounter another slime person. It’s a bit hard to make them out, as they are made of slime, in a slime tunnel, but the darker blue color stands out a bit amidst the greenish slime. You wonder if humanoid Slimes are aggressive, you suppose you’ll just ask, instead of just blasting them with magic. Actually, can you even cast magic down here? Fire would be an obvious no go, Ice might just get caught in all of this slime, and lightning... well, that’ll be the last thing you try down here.
\fiOooo,\fi what’s a precious little thing like you doing down here? Are you lost sweetie?
<CC Face: 1>Uh, yeah, I guess I am. I’ve got this collar on, so I can wander around down here, but I don’t really know where I’m going, or anything.

Oh, you’ve already got a collar? Let’s see, oh my, Nimh finally got one? Well, good for her. Just take your next right, and then a left, and her room will be at the end of that hallway. Let her know Sai’im would be interested in joining in, would you?
<CC Face: 1>Sure, I’ll get right on that, I guess.

Well, that was a bit cryptic, but at least you’ve got directions now. Plus, you didn’t have to electrocute yourself, so that went about as well as it could’ve. You should go find this “Nimh” now, you suppose.

You come to a... \fidoor?\fi Entrance? The end of the tunnel basically just has a door shaped area where the wall is replaced by a dark blue looking slime. It doesn’t have a door handle though, so you aren’t sure how it would open. You decide to try knocking on it instead. The slime is harder than it looks, so you are actually able to make some noise by pounding on it.

Instead of opening like, you know, a door, the darker color slime just fades until it’s the same as the slime you are currently submerged in, allowing the Slime girl who saved you from before to poke her head out.
Oh! W-What are you doing here? Actually, how are you even down here? Weren’t you drowning in our slime last time I found you?
<CC Face: 1>Yeah, I was, but I put on the collar you left behind, and suddenly I could \fionly\fi breathe slime.
The Slime girl, Nimh you suppose, starts shoving her arms \fiinto\fi her body frantically and wiggling them around, like she’s searching for something.
Ah! I really did lose it! What am I going to...
She cuts off, finally looking at your neck, as if just processing the part where you already told her you were wearing the damned thing. Her face turns deep blue as she starts to blush furiously.
<CC Face: 1>Should I have not put it on? Sorry about that, I guess.
Y-Yes, you d-definitely shouldn’t have put that on. I mean, it’s not like I really mind or anything, but...
<CC Face: 1>I have no idea what you are talking about here.
Oh, r-right, you probably can’t read what’s on the collar, can you? Well, how do I explain this in a way you’d understand... It uh, basically tells people that I own you.
O-Or more like my sex slave, maybe?
Well it’s just so nobody else tries to impregnate you! If you weren’t wearing it, you’d be \fiwell\fi on your way to being a mother, so don’t get mad at me!
You are stunned to silence at that, and it takes you a minute to find words once again.
<CC Face: 1>I can’t be a mother though.
Well, it’s not like how you humans do it. We raise our children as a community, you’d be less like a mother and more of a... breeding partner, I guess.
Great, so you’ve been wearing a collar that says “Nihm’s brood mare” all around the slime tunnels?
The point being that you wouldn’t be expected to raise the children yourself, we take care of our young ourselves.
<CC Face: 1>Okay, but that’s not what I meant. I can’t be a mother because I’m not a girl.
Oh, you aren’t? You totally looked like a female to me, my bad. I don’t see how that stops me from knocking you up though.
<CC Face: 1>I’m starting to get the feeling that the way you make babies is a lot different from the way we make babies.
Well, you aren’t made of slime, so I could see there being differences. Don’t you just dump your babies into someplace warm in your partner and wait for them to grow?
<CC Face: 1>N-No, uh, the “babies” need to go in the woman’s vagina, or else they don’t grow.
Huh, humans are weird. Can’t even put babies in a cute pair of balls.
<CC Face: 1>Y-You’d put them in my balls?!
Yep! Or, I guess your ass would work just fine as well. The babies are made of slime after all, it’s not like it matters how big the hole they come out of is.
<CC Face: 1>I suppose that’s true... Anyway, I guess it doesn’t matter since they all thought I was your... you know. I can just head on out of here now. And never come back.
Because I really want to knock you up!
<CC Face: 1>Well, this was fun, see ya.
You turn to leave, but Nimh lunges forward and grabs you by the arm, before dragging you back into her room and shutting the door.
<CC Face: 1>You know, I don’t think this is going to end well, but I’m starting to consider trying out lightning magic down here, what do you think?
N-No, wait, I-I’m sorry, just hear me out for a second, okay?
U-Um, well... \fipleeeeeease\fi let me fuck you!
Nimh wraps her arms around you and starts sobbing into your chest while she begs for you to mate with her. It’s sad to watch, honestly. After a little bit, she calms down enough to regain her senses.

I’m sorry, it’s just, I’m the \fionly\fi one around here who has \finever\fi had sex! Everyone always makes fun of me for being a virgin! All the adventurers who come through are either too sexy or too scary for me to approach! You are the first person of another species I’ve ever spoken to, if you don’t let me do it I never will!
<CC Face: 1>Even if you say that, I can’t adventure while pregnant, I can’t just put that on hold for months to have your kids.
Ah! That’s great then, because it only takes a few days for them to grow! So you can totally have my babies! Hooray!
...Fuck. She’s actually bouncing around her room in excitement.
So, how do you want to do it? I’ve always wanted to dump my load in a cute pair of balls, but since you are being so nice, I’m totally fine with doing it in the ass, if that’s what you are into.
<CC Face: 1>I never actually said I’d do it, you know?
What? B-But you said you didn’t want to because it would take too long, so what’s the problem.
<CC Face: 1>Maybe I just don’t want to have sex with you?
A-Am I that ugly... Even though it will feel super good for the both of us?
Great, she’s starting to cry now.
<CC Face: 1>How would you know it feels good for me too?

W-Well, the main reason we have these collars is because so many people come back over and over to get bred, if they didn’t have something to mark them, they’d get snatched up in a heartbeat. They wouldn’t come back if it didn’t feel good, would they?
<CC Face: 1>Er... I guess not. Unless they are getting paid for it, or something.
Nope, no payment, the pleasure is more than enough.
Nimh looks at you from the corner of her eye as she wipes the tears from her face. Well, are you going to break this poor slime girl’s heart, or become a mommy?
<CC Face: 1>I’m sorry Nimh, I just don’t think I’m ready for this.
O-Okay, I guess I’ll just be a virgin for life.
She seems to immediately get over it as she continues excitedly.
\fbBut!\fb If you ever change your mind and want to get bred by a Slime, you come to \fbME,\fb understand? I don’t want to hear you’ve slept with some slut like Sai’im, okay?
Oh, you’d forgotten about her. You decide to not tell her about Sai’im’s offer to join in, sounds like they don’t get along.
<CC Face: 1>Sure, if I ever came back, I’d be wearing your collar anyway, so it’s not like I’d have a choice.
Oh, hey, you're back!D-Did you wanna... maybe... you know... have sex?
Oh, hey, you're back!D-Did you wanna... maybe... you know... have more sex?

You don't think there's much for you to do this way, for the moment.
Hey, would you like a blowjob?
A blowjob. I hear you humans love those. I mean, I’ll just use my slime, so it’s not \fireally\fi a blowjob, but the idea is the same.
<CC Face: 1>Okay, but like, why? Most people don’t just offer random blowjobs.
Oh! Human semen contains valuable nutrition for us, it’s why the unevolved ones are so aggressive in the dungeon. I’ll get you off, you give me nutrients, everyone’s happy!
<CC Face: 1>I appreciate the offer, but I’m a bit busy at the moment, perhaps some other time.
I’ll be here whenever you feel the need!
You want another one? You aren't going to run out of goo, are you?
